# Fast POS — Production-Grade MSME Feature Expansion

## Goal

Add **8 high-impact, real-world features** that Indian MSME retailers genuinely need daily — features that showcase senior-level engineering: clean architecture, SOLID, Bloc-only state, 60fps UI, offline-first, and production hardening. No gimmicky AI — pure business utility.

---

## Summary of New Features

| # | Feature | Why It Matters |
|---|---------|----------------|
| 1 | **GST Invoice & Tax Engine** | Legal compliance — every registered MSME *must* file GST; current bills have zero tax support |
| 2 | **Multi-Unit / UOM Inventory** | Real shops sell in pieces, kg, litre, dozen, box — current system only tracks integer `stockQuantity` |
| 3 | **Purchase Orders & Supplier Management** | Shops restock from suppliers — there's no way to track inward stock, purchase cost, or supplier info |
| 4 | **Cash Register / Day Book (Khata)** | Every shopkeeper maintains a daily cash book — cash in, cash out, opening/closing balance |
| 5 | **Customer Loyalty & Rewards Program** | Entity has `loyaltyPoints` field but no rules, no earning/redemption — implement a full tier system |
| 6 | **Stock Audit & Physical Count** | Actual stock often differs from system — provide variance reconciliation with history |
| 7 | **Returns & Credit Notes** | Shops handle returns daily — zero support currently; must reverse stock + generate credit note |

