## Phased Rollout

### Phase 1 — Core Business (Features 1, 2, 7)
GST invoicing, multi-unit inventory, returns & credit notes. These are **table-stakes** for any real POS.

### Phase 2 — Operations (Features 3, 4, 6)
Purchase orders, day book, stock audit. These cover the **restock and reconciliation** cycle.

### Phase 3 — Growth (Feature 5)
Loyalty program. This is the **customer retention** layer.

