## Performance Guidelines (apply to all new code)

| Concern | Approach |
|---------|----------|
| **60fps lists** | `ListView.builder` + `itemExtent` for fixed-height rows; `RepaintBoundary` around complex cards |
| **Heavy computation** | Domain pure functions run in `compute()` isolate for >200 items (existing `core/isolate/` pattern) |
| **Bloc efficiency** | `Equatable` states with shallow equality; `transformEvents` with `debounce` for search inputs; `distinct()` on streams |
| **Widget rebuilds** | Extract `const` stateless widgets; use `BlocSelector` for fine-grained rebuilds instead of `BlocBuilder` on entire state |
| **Responsive** | Use existing `AppBreakpoints` — 1-column on phone, 2-column grid on tablet for forms |
| **Offline** | Hive cache for suppliers, purchase orders, cash entries; sync outbox pattern matching existing `OfflineFirstBillsRepository` |
| **Memory** | Dispose all stream subscriptions in `close()`; use `addPostFrameCallback` for deferred work |

